      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes sense that your brain is telling you the truth right now, because the pain of losing everything feels permanent and the shame is real. The fact that you are still thinking about how to fix this and about your loved ones proves you care deeply, even if it hurts you to admit it. You are not a stain on their lives; you are the very person who built their world, and their love for you is not conditional on your success.",
